{"tid":168210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國上海一間公司宣布強制「停工一周玩遊戲」　違者直接開除","createTime":"2017-03-23T11:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T20:09:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1318eee6e87ac2ea0552c7532ea39feae6b87b38","tid":168210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"2017-03-23 06:54 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n怎麼有公司要員工休假一周玩遊戲呢？日前中國上海一間電子商務公司員工爆料，公司發公告要求員工從早上6時到晚上12時，參加阿里釘釘企業開工狂歡月砸錘子遊戲，且不得請假、遲到早退，「拒絕的人直接辦理離職手續」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/23/850590-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F850590-XXL.jpg&h=3d1167f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲電子商務公司公告停工一周。（圖／翻攝自《中華網》）</span><br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒《中華網》報導，上海該間電子商務公司日前在公告上提到，「因市場低迷，為提升公司經營利潤」，要求員工從20日開始，休假一周都去玩遊戲，遊戲所得獎品全歸公司所有，且每天早6到晚12不得請假、遲到早退，不答應的人可以直接辦理離職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/23/850584-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F850584-XXL.jpg&h=e3818503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲員工聊天討論停工一周玩遊戲。（圖／翻攝自《中華網》）</span><br />\n<br />\n該公司發言人透露，經公司管理層和財務核算研究決定，因玩遊戲獲得的獎品比業務員的銷售額還高，所以公告停工一周讓員工玩遊戲。目前該公司員工也真的加入砸錘子遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=236180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D236180&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=90210a72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D236180&h=f33916d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=236180</a>"},{"pid":"3c395a6d44dfa88e3e4b4afc5548aab8b40d13d9","tid":168210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e59ab4d677f63c4ecc5ef5cdfe6259885f52d25","tid":168210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6475d6518237585469c720d72783d9218a4e81","tid":168210,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T19:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9542380c0776b859629ddbe4c059bdf21d71806","tid":168210,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T20:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2017-03-23 06:54 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n怎麼有公司要員工休假一周玩遊戲呢？日前中國上海一間電子商務公司員工爆料，公司發公告要求員工從早上6時到晚上12時，參加阿里釘釘企業開工狂歡月砸錘子遊戲，且不得請假、遲到早退，「拒絕的人直接辦理離職手續」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/23/850590-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F850590-XXL.jpg&h=3d1167f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲電子商務公司公告停工一周。（圖／翻攝自《中華網》）</span><br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒《中華網》報導，上海該間電子商務公司日前在公告上提到，「因市場低迷，為提升公司經營利潤」，要求員工從20日開始，休假一周都去玩遊戲，遊戲所得獎品全歸公司所有，且每天早6到晚12不得請假、遲到早退，不答應的人可以直接辦理離職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/03/23/850584-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2F850584-XXL.jpg&h=e3818503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲員工聊天討論停工一周玩遊戲。（圖／翻攝自《中華網》）</span><br />\n<br />\n該公司發言人透露，經公司管理層和財務核算研究決定，<span style=\"color: red;\">因玩遊戲獲得的獎品比業務員的銷售額還高</span>，所以公告停工一周讓員工玩遊戲。目前該公司員工也真的加入砸錘子遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=236180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D236180&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=90210a72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D236180&h=f33916d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=236180</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}